org.youscope.addon.microplate

Interface MicroplateAddonFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnsiSBSMicroplateTypeFactory, BDBioscienceMultiwellTCMicroplateTypeFactory, CustomMicroplateTypeFactory

    public interface MicroplateAddonFactory
    Factory to create layouts of microplates, i.e. how many wells they have, how they are layouted, and how big they are.
    Author:
    Moritz Lang

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      Returns a new MicroplateType for the given type identifier, or throws an AddonException if this factory does not support microplates with the given type identifier.

      • createMicroplateType

        Microplate createMicroplateType(java.lang.String typeIdentifier)
                         throws AddonException
        Returns a new MicroplateType for the given type identifier, or throws an AddonException if this factory does not support microplates with the given type identifier.

        typeIdentifier - The type identifier of a microplate for which the definition should be returned.
